<dl id="n12123j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12123j">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12123j"> 123(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> menhir grow smaller</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">It is equally difficult to understand why the large menhirs are always placed near a cromlech and why the menhirs themselves take an easterly direction and <mark>gradually diminish in size</mark>. <small> Zacharie Le Rouzic, <a name="MMCL" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#MMCL"><cite title="source">The Megalithic Monuments of Carnac and Locmariaquer</cite></a> (1908) s 28</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c12127g" href="c12all.htm#c12127g">VI.C.12:127(g)</a></mm></dd> </dd></dl>
